quran[4]{c,v,t}:
  4,97,Those vita terminated angels dum dictus de wronging their anima angels ask them Quod est the matter vos? They dictus Nos oppressed terra. They dictus Est deus terra non spacious satis vos emigrate therein? these ultimus abode est Hell miserable destiny
  4,98,Exempted est infirmus vir femina infans non possess strength nor means invenit via
  4,99,These pardoned DEUS. DEUS est Pardoner Forgiver
  4,100,Anyone emigrates causa de DEUS testimentum invenit terra major bounties richness! Anyone dedit up his domus emigrating DEUS His messenger tunc decessus catches up cum eum his recompense reserved DEUS! DEUS est Forgiver Merciful